						               													<description>Kickstarter Exclusive that brings a whole new feature to the game in the form of adorable and resourceful Companions to help the Heroes in their battles. From a loyal telepathic dog to a deceitfully cute &amp;ldquo;cat&amp;rdquo;, with maybe a land shark or frog in the mix as well, these little critters will stand united!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Companions is a new feature players can choose to add to their game, giving them more options and strategies (plus an adorable sidekick). If a Hero chooses to take a Companion with them, they simply shuffle the 3 Companion cards into their Hero deck and place the Companion&amp;rsquo;s game piece next to their Hero. Every turn, the player can move their Companion one Location for free. While Companions are not considered Heroes (they don&amp;rsquo;t take damage or suffer other effects), they do provide company so Heroes don&amp;rsquo;t count as being &amp;ldquo;alone&amp;rdquo; in their Location. Companion cards work just like Hero cards, providing an Action to the Hero and a Special Effect to their Companion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Pet Companions Kickstarter Exclusive expansion comes with:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1 Redwing Game Piece&amp;#10;1 Goose Game Piece&amp;#10;1 Jeffrey Game Piece&amp;#10;1 Throg Game Piece&amp;#10;1 Cosmo Game Piece&amp;#10;1 Alligator Loki Game Piece&amp;#10;3 Redwing Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Goose Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Jeffrey Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Throg Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Cosmo Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Alligator Loki Companion Cards&amp;#10;3 Lockheed Companion Cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
